  <h1 class="text-center mb-4">About</h1>

  <h2>General Information</h2>
  <p>Welcome to <strong>Soon</strong>, a vibrant social media platform designed to connect people, ideas, and communities in meaningful ways. Our mission is to create a space where users can express themselves freely, engage with diverse perspectives, and build authentic connections.</p>

  <p>At <strong>Soon</strong>, we believe that every individual has a unique story to tell. Our platform empowers users to share their passions, creativity, and knowledge with a global audience. From posting captivating photos and videos to engaging in thoughtful discussions, <strong>Soon</strong> offers a dynamic environment for self-expression.</p>

  <h2>Our Vision</h2>
  <p>Our vision is to create a digital space where authenticity thrives. We aim to foster a community built on trust, respect, and inclusivity. We strive to be more than just a platform — we want to be a catalyst for positive change, a space where users feel safe, inspired, and heard.</p>

  <h2>What Makes Us Different</h2>
  <p>Unlike conventional social media platforms, <strong>Soon</strong> prioritizes user well-being. Our platform is designed with advanced privacy controls, customizable content preferences, and smart algorithms that reduce harmful content. Our goal is to promote healthier online interactions and reduce digital fatigue.</p>

  <h2>Core Features</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Content Sharing:</strong> Share images, videos, and posts with your friends, followers, or the wider community.</li>
    <li><strong>Customizable Feed:</strong> Personalize your content feed to see only what matters to you.</li>
    <li><strong>Interactive Tools:</strong> Use stickers, filters, and creative editing features to enhance your content.</li>
    <li><strong>Community Groups:</strong> Join interest-based groups to connect with like-minded people.</li>
    <li><strong>Privacy First:</strong> Control who sees your content and how your personal data is used.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Our Commitment to Safety</h2>
  <p>We are committed to providing a secure and inclusive platform for everyone. Our moderation team and AI-powered tools work around the clock to detect and prevent harmful behavior such as bullying, harassment, and misinformation. Our reporting system is transparent, ensuring users have a voice in maintaining the safety of the community.</p>

  <h2>Join Us Today</h2>
  <p>Be a part of the <strong>Soon</strong> community and experience social media in a new way. Connect with people who inspire you, explore content that sparks curiosity, and contribute to a healthier digital environment. Whether you’re here to create, connect, or simply be inspired, <strong>Soon</strong> is where your story begins.</p>

  <p>Your voice matters. Your ideas matter. And at <strong>Soon</strong>, you matter.</p>

