  <p class="contact">Have questions, suggestions, or feedback? We’d love to hear from you! Reach out to our support team at <a href="mailto:contact@soon.com">contact@soon.com</a> or visit our Help Center for more information.</p>

  <p class="contact">Join the movement. Join <strong>Soon</strong>.<br>Where Connections Come to Life.</p>
